   </tr>\n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>\n                </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <h1>Beille 2pc Cream Terry Quilted Oven Mitts Set Baking Supplies, 14 Inch Length (One Size Fits All)</h1>\n                <h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">24.99</span></h2>\n                <p>A kitchen staple, elevated. The Beille 2pc Terry Oven Mitts Set in off white, cream color bring everyday function and soft, neutral style to any kitchen. Made with a plush terry cloth quilted interior and exterior for added structure and comfort, these long oven mitts offer reliable protection whether you’re pulling out a hot casserole or lifting a fresh pie from the oven.\n\nEach quilted oven mitt measures 14 inches in length, offering extended coverage to shield your hands and lower arms from heat. The soft yet durable design fits most hands comfortably and securely, making the oven mitts a must have tool for cooking, baking, and hosting alike!\n\nBeautifully simple and thoughtfully designed, these oven mitts blend seamlessly into any kitchen. Pair them with your favorite Beille kitchen tools for a cohesive, consciously curated space. Machine washable and made to withstand repeated use, this terry oven mitt set combines practicality with an inviting kitchen aesthetic. Reliable, stylish, and always ready to handle the heat.</p>\n                <div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n                    <div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-100\">\n                        <p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n                        <p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n                        <a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebsto